SE*12*10695~
ST*301*10696~
B1***20130225*U~
Y3*"&amp;BookingRefNo&amp;"*"&amp;operatorCode&amp;"*20130226*20130318~
N1*SH*FOREST PRODUCTS~
R4*L*K*NZPOE*MOBILE, AL*US~
R4*D*K*MYTPP*ROTTERDAM*NL~
R4*N***VELSEN~
Y4*10275929****1*45R1*SEFN***D/P~
N7*TRIU*863598********************45R1**45R0~
N9*EQP*TRIU-863598-9~
LX*0~
W09*CZ*-4*FA******~
